{"prompt": "Develop an engaging platform for a creative writing workshop. The primary color should be a deep plum.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Creative Writing Workshop</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #6a0dad; /* Deep Plum */\n            --secondary-color: #e6dff2; /* Light Lavender */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --accent-color: #f0e8f8;\n        }\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n        header {\n            background: var(--primary-color);\n            color: #fff;\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: #e6dff2 3px solid;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        #main-content {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n            gap: 20px;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n        .intro-section, .workshop-details, .community-section, .cta-section {\n            background: #fff;\n            padding: 25px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n        }\n        .intro-section {\n            flex: 2;\n            min-width: 300px;\n        }\n        .workshop-details {\n            flex: 1;\n            min-width: 250px;\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary-color), #8a2be2); /* Gradient */\n            color: #fff;\n        }\n        .workshop-details h3 {\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 0;\n        }\n        .workshop-details ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            padding: 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .workshop-details li {\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        .community-section {\n            flex: 1;\n            min-width: 250px;\n        }\n        .cta-section {\n            flex: 2;\n            min-width: 300px;\n            text-align: center;\n            background: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n        h2, h3 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n        .btn {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background: var(--primary-color);\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n            border: none;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n        .btn:hover {\n            background: #8a2be2; /* Slightly darker plum */\n        }\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            background: var(--primary-color);\n            color: #fff;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n        .highlight {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n        #writing-prompts li {\n            position: relative;\n            padding-left: 20px;\n            margin-bottom: 8px;\n        }\n        #writing-prompts li::before {\n            content: '\u2712\ufe0f'; /* Pen emoji */\n            position: absolute;\n            left: 0;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Ink & Imagination</h1>\n            <p>Your Hub for Creative Writing Exploration</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"main-content\">\n            <article class=\"intro-section\">\n                <h2>Unleash Your Inner Author</h2>\n                <p>Welcome to Ink & Imagination, a vibrant online space designed for writers of all levels. Whether you're just starting your journey or looking to refine your craft, our platform offers resources, community, and inspiration to help your stories come to life.</p>\n                <p>Dive into a world where words take flight. Explore different genres, participate in engaging discussions, and get constructive feedback from fellow creatives.</p>\n            </article>\n\n            <aside class=\"workshop-details\">\n                <h3>Upcoming Workshops</h3>\n                <ul>\n                    <li><strong>Character Development:</strong> July 15th</li>\n                    <li><strong>Plotting Your Novel:</strong> July 22nd</li>\n                    <li><strong>Poetry Slam Prep:</strong> July 29th</li>\n                </ul>\n                <p style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;\"><button class=\"btn\">View Schedule</button></p>\n            </aside>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"writing-prompts\" class=\"intro-section\" style=\"margin-top: 20px;\">\n            <h2>Daily Writing Prompts</h2>\n            <ul>\n                <li>Write a story about a forgotten object that suddenly gains consciousness.</li>\n                <li>Describe a city where emotions manifest as weather patterns.</li>\n                <li>Imagine a conversation between the moon and a lonely lighthouse keeper.</li>\n                <li>Craft a poem from the perspective of a shadow.</li>\n            </ul>\n            <p style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;\"><button class=\"btn\">More Prompts</button></p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"community-section\" class=\"community-section\" style=\"margin-top: 20px;\">\n            <h2>Join the Conversation</h2>\n            <p>Connect with a supportive community of writers. Share your work, offer critiques, and find critique partners. Our forums are buzzing with activity!</p>\n            <p style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;\"><button class=\"btn\">Join Forum</button></p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"cta-section\" style=\"margin-top: 20px;\">\n            <h2>Ready to Write Your Next Chapter?</h2>\n            <p>Sign up today and gain access to exclusive resources, workshops, and our thriving writing community.</p>\n            <p><button class=\"btn\">Get Started Now</button></p>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Ink & Imagination. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Simple JS for interactive elements if needed in future\n        document.querySelectorAll('.btn').forEach(button => {\n            button.addEventListener('click', () => {\n                alert('Action triggered! (More features coming soon)');\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}